OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,FThree MPs including Culture Secretary
OL,7,FLisa Nandy have called on the
OL,8,FGovernment to release a "promised" #6m
OL,9,Fin Levelling Up cash.
OL,11,FThe Labour representatives for Wigan
OL,12,Fwrote to the Deputy Prime Minister
OL,13,FAngela Rayner to explain how payment
OL,14,Fdelays could force the local council
OL,15,Fto borrow money as a "last resort".
OL,17,FWigan Council planned to use the
OL,18,FLevelling Up money to fund major
OL,19,Fprojects, including the Haigh Hall
OL,20,Frenovation which is already well
OL,21,Funderway.
