OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,FWigan MP Lisa Nandy, Leigh's Jo Platt
OL,7,Fand Makerfield's Josh Simons have
OL,8,Fjointly signed the letter to Ms Rayner.
OL,10,FIn the letter, they wrote: "Working
OL,11,Fpeople across the country,
OL,12,Fparticularly in small towns like ours,
OL,13,Fwere promised we would be levelled up.
OL,15,F"That never happened. Instead, they
OL,16,Fwere given stagnation, poorer living
OL,17,Fstandards and fewer opportunities.
