OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,F"Supporting towns must be at the heart
OL,7,Fof our strategy for growth. Wigan
OL,8,FCouncil has received notification from
OL,9,Fyour department informing them of a
OL,10,Fdelay in payments of Levelling Up
OL,11,Fscheme money of around two months."
OL,13,FThe MPs say that Wigan Council has
OL,14,Fbeen told there will be a two month
OL,15,Fdelay to the payment from the Housing,
OL,16,FCommunities and Local Government
OL,17,Fdepartment.
OL,19,FHaigh Hall's restoration has been
OL,20,Fongoing since it became publicly owned
OL,21,Fin 2021.
