OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,FAs one of Wigan's most historic sites,
OL,7,Fthe #37.5m transformation aims to
OL,8,F"repair and restore Haigh Hall to its
OL,9,Fformer glory, ensuring residents and
OL,10,Fvisitors can enjoy one of the
OL,11,Fborough's most significant landmarks."
OL,13,FThe letter goes on: "This has
OL,14,Fsignificant impacts on the three
OL,15,Fschemes in our area, across Haigh
OL,16,FHall, Leigh and Ashton-in-Makerfield.
OL,17,FHaigh Hall's works are already
OL,18,Funderway, and the other two are in the
OL,19,Fearly delivery phases.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
