OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,F"The cash flow implications of this
OL,7,Fwould have a significant impact on the
OL,8,Fcouncil's capacity to continue these
OL,9,Fworks.
OL,11,F"The second quarter claim would be in
OL,12,Fthe region of #6m which the council
OL,13,Fhas already funded and will need to
OL,14,Fclaim retrospectively.
OL,16,F"The Council cannot afford to have
OL,17,Fthat #6 million delayed, especially
OL,18,Fgiven the expenditure has already
OL,19,Foccurred.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
