OL,3,C'Hand over #6m in Levelling Up cash
OL,4,Cfor town now': MPs' plea for money
OL,6,F"Wigan council are extremely concerned
OL,7,Fabout the prospect of having to borrow
OL,8,Fthis money as a last resort. In the
OL,9,Fupcoming budget, we urge you to ensure
OL,10,Fthat already struggling local
OL,11,Fauthorities are not pushed over the
OL,12,Fbrink.
OL,14,F"Ashton-in-Makerfield, Wigan and Leigh
OL,15,Fwere promised funding for major local
OL,16,Fprojects. Work has already begun. It
OL,17,Fis vital that we support that and do
OL,18,Fnot leave our proud towns in an
OL,19,Fimpossible position.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
